column2: SELECT up_id,  dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq( up_ra,up_dec,up_sep ) as objId   FROM #upload  WHERE  dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq( up_ra,up_dec,up_sep ) IS NOT NULL  SELECT TOP #   p.ra,p.dec, p.run,p.rerun,p.camCol,p.field,p.obj,cast(str(p.ra,#,#) as float) as ra,cast(str(p.[dec],#,#) as float) as dec,dbo.fIAUFromEq(p.ra,p.[dec]) as SDSSname,p.deVAB_i,p.deVAB_r,p.deVABErr_i,p.deVABErr_r,p.deVPhi_i,p.deVPhi_r,p.r,ISNULL(s.z,#) as redshift  FROM ..PhotoObj AS p  LEFT OUTER JOIN ..SpecObj s ON p.objID = s.bestObjID  JOIN #x AS x ON x.objID=p.objID  JOIN #upload AS u ON u.up_id = x.up_id   WHERE  ( p.type = # OR p.type = #)   ORDER BY x.up_id
